nodes.class_name:
CompleteTableDetectionSystem(
  (feature_processor): Sequential(
    (0): Conv2d(20, 64, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    (1): BatchNorm2d(64, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (2): ReLU()
    (3): Conv2d(64, 64, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
    (4): BatchNorm2d(64, eps=1e-05, momentum=0.1, affine=True, track_running_stats=True)
    (5): ReLU()
  )
  (rpn): RegionProposalNetwork(
    (feature_extractor): Sequential(
      (0): Conv2d(64, 64, kernel_size=(3, 3), stride=(1, 1), padding=(1, 1))
      (1): ReLU()
    )
    (classification_head): Conv2d(64, 72, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
    (regression_head): Conv2d(64, 144, kernel_size=(1, 1), stride=(1, 1))
  )
  (roi_align): ROIAlign()
  (detection_head): TableDetectionHead(
    (shared_network): Sequential(
      (0): Flatten(start_dim=1, end_dim=-1)
      (1): Linear(in_features=3136, out_features=1024, bias=True)
      (2): ReLU()
      (3): Dropout(p=0.5, inplace=False)
      (4): Linear(in_features=1024, out_features=512, bias=True)
      (5): ReLU()
      (6): Dropout(p=0.5, inplace=False)
    )
    (classifier): Linear(in_features=512, out_features=2, bias=True)
    (bbr_head): Linear(in_features=512, out_features=4, bias=True)
    (pbr_head): Sequential(
      (0): Linear(in_features=512, out_features=256, bias=True)
      (1): ReLU()
      (2): Linear(in_features=256, out_features=4, bias=True)
    )
  )
)
